      "author": "band",
      "description": "Obsidian plugin that:\r\n1. creates and updates Folder Filelist indicies containing wikilinks to the files in the specified folders.\r\n2. installl a `ribbonIcon` button that updates these indicies when selected.\r\n\r\nThe folder filelist is a simple list of wikilinks in reverse modification time order - newest first.  \r\n\r\nCustom headers for the index files can be stored in an `.indexHeading.md` file in folders specified as includedFolders in the plugin settings. Default headings are generated if no such file exists.  \r\n\r\nTODO: review performance and review how Obsidian create, delete, rename, and modify events are handled.\r\n",
